signatureAbility.signatureDescription: True legendary receivers make the impossible possible. When they enter the zone, they have greatly increased success rate on aggressive catches of 50+ yards regardless of coverage.
When lined up in the slot, players with this ability have access to four additional hot routes during pre-play adjustments.
When lined up in the slot, receivers with this ability make faster cuts and have better hands on short routes.
Aggressive receivers overpower defenders and attack the football. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their success rate on aggressive catches against single coverage.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running streak routes.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running curl or comeback routes.
Defenders with this ability can still tackle effectively while trying to strip the football.
Defenders with this ability don't allow broken tackles when hit-sticking ballcarriers - regardless of the runner's size or power.

signatureAbility.signatureActivationDescription: Make consecutive passes for 5+ yards in air
signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Fearless quarterbacks are unintimidated by the pass rush. When they enter the zone, their passing accuracy is unaffected by defensive pressure.
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all lob or touch passes (except high/low and cross-body throws).
While in the pocket, passers with this ability are almost guaranteed to break the first sack attempt by a blitzing defensive back.
When playing at home, players with this ability can easily enter the Zone.
Passers with this ability have extended range on all unpressured precision passing from the pocket (except on high/low throws).
Some players thrive on making defenders look silly. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their fakeout rate on the next juke, spin or hurdle.
Ballcarriers with this ability have faster spin animations.
Defenders with this ability have an increased success rate when using conservative or diving tackles.
